Yes, this stuff is off in the future.

83
00:03:19.100 --> 00:03:21.920
But now is the time to
start brainstorming.

84
00:03:21.920 --> 00:03:23.970
Because things are moving fast.

85
00:03:23.970 --> 00:03:26.920
Position yourself to be
ready and at the forefront.

86
00:03:26.920 --> 00:03:29.790
Your brand could get a huge PR bump

87
00:03:29.790 --> 00:03:32.700
by being the first to try something.

88
00:03:32.700 --> 00:03:35.950
What might you offer
that could make a splash?

89
